路易斯·沃尔什承认在《Boyzone》预告片中编造了新闻报道https://www.nme.com/news/tv/louis-walsh-admits-making-up-press-stories-in-boyzone-doc-trailer-3830823?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=louis-walsh-admits- Boyzone 文档预告片中的化妆新闻故事Victoria LuxfordTue, 21 Jan 2025 17:08:18 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV NewsUncategorisedPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3830823 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="男孩地带" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我从来没有为此感到内疚”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/louis-walsh-admits-making-up-press-stories-in-boyzone-doc-trailer-3830823">Louis Walsh 承认在 Boyzone 文档预告片中编造新闻报道的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="男孩地带" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Louis-Walsh-X-Factor-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boyzone">Boyzone 的</a>前经纪人路易斯·沃尔什 (Louis Walsh) 承认在纪录片<em>《Boyzone: No Matter What》</em>的新预告片中捏造了有关乐队的故事以引起媒体关注。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/opinion/the-x-factor-cancelled-simon-cowell-3007510">《X Factor》在 17 年后退出：这才是真正扼杀歌唱真人秀节目的原因</a></li></ul><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/boyzone-no-matter-what-doc-trailer-promises-heartbreak-and-tabloid-scandal-3829649">天空纪录片 2 月 2 日开始播放</a>的节目片段中，沃尔什被描述为“新闻界的傀儡大师”，随后沃尔什本人也承认，他会不惜一切代价来获得媒体对乐队的报道。</p><p>他透露：“有时，男孩们会在报纸上读到一些关于自己的不真实的故事，他们会说‘谁告诉他们的？’。”我做到了！我告诉他们”。 Boyzone 歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ronan-keating">罗南·基廷 (Ronan Keating)</a>阐述道：“他相信任何故事都是好故事。他会不断编造关于乐队的故事，关于与不存在的女友关系的故事”。</p><p>在最极端的例子之一中，沃尔什回忆起编造了一个关于乐队遭遇飞机事故的故事。 “有一次我在澳大利亚让他们遭遇了一场空难，我忘记告诉家人我编造了这一切”，他笑着回忆起这段回忆，然后承认：“虽然没有发生空难，但它有一个很好的故事”。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/DFFxgLAIoss/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; w